{{Infobox dungeon |name = New Mauville |image = [[File:New Mauville.png|300px]] |caption = An inside view of New Mauville. |tokens = 24,000 |location = South of Mauville City, East of Route 110. }} '''New Mauville''' is a [[Dungeons|dungeon]] in [[Hoenn]]. It initially has 49 tiles arranged in a 7x7 square, including 7 chest tiles, 17 non-boss encounter tiles, and 1 boss encounter tile. Wild Encounters have 460,000 HP.
